de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.im.evaluate

Interface ImEvaluationUnit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ImEvaluationComponent<ImAttribute>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ImcEvaluationUnit, ImvEvaluationUnit
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractImcEvaluationUnitIetf, AbstractImEvaluationUnitIetf, DefaultImcEvaluationUnit, DefaultImvEvaluationUnit

    interface ImEvaluationUnit
extends ImEvaluationComponent<ImAttribute>
    Generic evaluation unit base. The evaluation unit is responsible to measure/evaluate a certain aspect of a component (e.g. the version of the anti-virus software for the anti-virus component).

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      long getType()
      Returns the type ID, that specifies the measured aspect (e.g. the product information aspect type from the IETF).
      long getVendorId()
      Returns the vendor ID, that specifies the measured aspect (e.g. an aspect specified by the IETF).
